Vacation Rentals
Review a vacation rental
We’ll remind you to review your stay throughout your trip. Once you check out, follow the steps below to leave your review.  
You can also review any rental you stayed at in the last two years. 
Here’s how it works: 
Find the listing of the rental you stayed at and select Write a Review. You’ll be taken to the Tripadvisor reviews page. 
You’ll be asked to rate the rental and leave your review. 
When you’re done, Submit your review and sign in to your Tripadvisor account (or your Facebook or Google account, if you prefer). 
We’ll email you to confirm your review has been submitted 
The review will be published on the listing, and the owner will have the chance to respond. 
All traveler reviews must comply with our guidelines and be written by confirmed guests.
